            <description><![CDATA[【“34岁社恐，刚做完开脑手术，医生给我过海底捞生日”<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[单身狗]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/_/co_niuec-7d05bc992a.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】一股让社恐瑟瑟发抖的海底捞“庆生潮”最近也刮到了深圳一家医院，原来是一位潮汕资娘仔，在生日前一天做了开脑手术醒来2礼拜后，意外收到一群白大褂“海底捞”式的献唱与祝福！原本可能非死即残的她，那一刻竟然能手抱着花俯身一口吹熄蜡烛，实现了她手术前一刻曾忐忑告诉医生的心愿——“我想过我34岁生日。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[泪]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_lei-4cdf6ee412.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>”<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E6%95%85%E4%BA%8B%E6%B1%87%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E6%95%85%E4%BA%8B%E6%B1%87%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫科普故事汇#</span></a><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hhzdj69jqtj20u059lwtw.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hhzdj56xttj20g92zegsy.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hhzdj56aw3j20g938b7bm.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hhzdj5jhdvj20g9516wqh.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hhzdj5d2njj20g92zmn4v.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hhzdj70hewg20fn08rkjo.gif" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
